Release Notes for Version 3.12.1
================================

Overview
--------

Release 3.12.1 is the 2nd release in the Errata Tool 3.12 development period.
It closes [34 bugs and RFEs][buglist].

This release of Errata Tool includes phase one of CDN Content Availability
Testing (CCAT) and a number of fixes and enhancements related to UX, and
service integrations.

